con:config.con:query: Select Distinct s.Pro_NB,s.Shipment_key, s.M204_SHP_TAG_ID,scr1.M204_BUS_TAG_ID, sc1.Business_NM, sc1.Street_Address_TX, sc1.City_NM, sc1.State_Province_Abbreviation_CD, sc1.Postal_CD From SHIP.Shipment s Left Outer Join SHIP.Shipment_Customer_Role_VW scr1 On scr1.Shipment_KEY = s.Shipment_KEY And ((scr1.Customer_Role_Type_CD = 'C' Or scr1.Customer_Role_Type_CD = 'R')) Left Outer Join SHIP.Shipment_Customer_VW sc1 On (sc1.Shipment_Customer_Role_KEY = scr1.Shipment_Customer_Role_KEY) Where s.Pro_NB = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}'

Select m.WGP_ID_NBR, m.WGP_SHP_TAG,s.[SHP_BUS_TAG], s.SHP_NM_RPRTD, s.SHP_STREET_RPRTD, s.SHP_CITY_RPRTD, s.SHP_ST_ABBR_RPRTD, s.SHP_ZIP_RPRTD From Legacy.M204_WGP m Left Outer Join Legacy.M204_BSR s On m.WGP_SHP_TAG = s.SHP_TAG And ((s.SHP_BUS_ROLE = 'C' Or s.SHP_BUS_ROLE = 'R')) Where m.WGP_ID_NBR = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}'
